# This repo's whole point is the .cursor/ framework, but Cursor dirs are often
# ignored globally. Re-include it here, then re-ignore the live-data files below.
!.cursor/

# Live data — generated locally by `bash .cursor/dev/setup.sh`. Never commit these:
# they hold your actual tasks, goals, and ADO details. Leading `/` anchors to the
# repo root so the stub copies under .cursor/dev/bootstrap/ are still tracked.
/01-todos.md
/02-inbox.md
/04-goals.md
/05-done.csv
.cursor/sync-state.md
.cursor/ado-config.md
.cursor/ado/target.md

# Personal project detail under 03-projects/ (keep the README template)
03-projects/*.md
!03-projects/README.md
